<ab facs="#facs_572_r1l26">ſagt . vvie Jr in darynne gar hılfflich vnd <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_572_r1l27">geweſen 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſein </del> ſeit / des vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit vnd <expan>freuntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab>
